<div class="site-header">
  <h1>South Portland's Flock Safety Camera Network</h1>
  <p>FOAA-obtained audit log data — independently verifiable</p>
</div>

<p>South Portland Police Department (SPPD) runs Flock Safety automated license plate readers. FOAA requests revealed that <strong>602+ agencies</strong> across <strong>44 states</strong> have access to SPPD's camera data. Over <strong>2,000 searches</strong> have been logged since April 2025, including cross-agency lookups and searches for ICE.</p>

